name: Fatman Scoop
summary: Beloved rapper Fatman Scoop, renowned for his energetic performances, tragically passed away at age 53 after suffering a medical emergency while performing in Hamden, Connecticut. According to eyewitness accounts, the rapper collapsed onstage during his set and was immediately administered CPR. Despite medical efforts, Scoop was pronounced deceased at a local hospital. The news of his passing has sent shockwaves through the entertainment industry and his fans worldwide, who mourn the loss of a beloved hip-hop icon.

summary: The 2024 Notre Dame football schedule is set, with dates, times, TV channels, and scores available on NCAA.com. Among the notable games are the season opener against Texas A&M in primetime, which will be televised on ESPN and can be streamed on WatchESPN, fuboTV, Hulu, and YouTube TV. Other notable games include a home contest against Clemson on November 2 and a rivalry game against USC on November 30. The new College Football Playoff format, which expands to 12 teams, could have a major impact on Notre Dame's chances of making the playoffs. The Irish are also hoping to build on their 2023 success with a strong showing in 2024, and Marcus Freeman is aiming to prove himself as a top coach. Fans can also catch a new series on Notre Dame football called "Here Come the Irish" on Peacock.

name: The Deliverance
summary: "The Deliverance," a new horror film on Netflix, has garnered mixed reactions. The New York Times praises its compelling campiness while PureWow deems it a terrifying experience for fans of "The Exorcist." TIME delves into the real-life demonic possession case that inspired the movie. Crooked Marquee and Northdallasgazette offer critical reviews, highlighting the film's shortcomings. TODAY provides a detailed explanation of the ambiguous ending, while SLUG Magazine shares a more favorable perspective. TheOnlyCritic finds the cast strong but unable to redeem the mediocre story. Variety sheds light on the impact the film had on its director, Lee Daniels, whose mother feared he might be cursed. USA TODAY explores the haunting true story that serves as the film's basis. Overall, "The Deliverance" evokes a range of opinions, from enthusiastic praise to cautious criticism, suggesting that it may leave viewers divided.

name: Venezuelan gangs
summary: Reports indicate that violence involving Venezuelan gangs has spread into suburban areas from a neighboring sanctuary city, despite attempts to restrict migrant entry. In the Denver metropolitan area, there have been concerns about Venezuelan gang activity, with the mayor of Aurora expressing frustration over a "failed policy." While the city of Aurora has acknowledged the presence of "components" of the Tren de Aragua gang, it claims that reports of their influence are isolated. Police have responded to concerns about Venezuelan gangs in Colorado, and a video of armed gang members in an apartment went viral. The mayor of Aurora has admitted to the presence of Venezuelan gangs in apartment complexes in the city, and Homeland Security sources have confirmed the presence of gang members in a video. However, the mayors of Denver and Aurora have criticized exaggerated coverage of migrant gang activity as creating "hysteria."

name: Coco Gauff
summary: On Day 3 of the US Open, defending champion Coco Gauff had a successful start with an easy win, marking an end to her two-match losing streak. However, her title defense faces a tougher path ahead. Gauff initially faced a slow start against Elina Svitolina, but rallied to advance to the fourth round. She credits a comment on TikTok for shifting her perspective. Despite the uneven start, Gauff regained form and cruised into the third round. Her resurgence included an emphatic victory, which she attributes to improved serving. As the defending champion, Gauff's performance has been closely watched, and her progression into the fourth round keeps her title hopes alive.
